  "texts": [
    "2 Classification of ML techniques [15] of individual models is created by combining several weak classifiers together.",
    "Methods like bagging and boosting are examples of group learning procedures [14].Various ML algorithms have shown a vital role for developing efficient models for detecting cyberattaks and fraud.",
    "For example, Linear Classifiers (LC) which are linear algorithms, use decision boundaries to separate input vectors into classes.",
    "This classification aims to gather similar features together into categories [16].",
    "In classification issues, Logistic Regression (LR) approach is used to predict the outcome for a categorical dependent variable."
  ]
}